{"title":"桅杆","authors":["蔺洪生"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":10,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"桅杆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔺洪生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你以视野作底片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用起伏的潮汐押韵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"携一路烈风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"携慷慨的阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在开阔得没有尽头的海面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树立起华表般巍峨的主题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你沉默如丰碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给汹涌的世界留下美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你美在一个高起点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美在弄潮儿胜券在握的部分"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美在披一身海浪花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美在时间摧不倒的坚韧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你与白帆的爱情永远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平仄成音乐的姿势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和永无休止的跋涉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"令海鸥的劲翼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化成火热的诗行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当你向彼岸出征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收获的季节便如期而至"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}